snippet.title: Metagates Beta Testing
snippet.description: Metagates is an open-world MMORPG with a social hub city that features PvP arenas and PvE dungeons. Explore our dynamic world where you can gather, craft, and trade equipment and materials in our deeply immersive world rich in lore, storytelling, and science.
